com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils

Class AssetDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils.AssetDescriptor

  • @Immutable
public final class AssetDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Returns a descriptor of the asset which includes the file name and version as mandatory fields. The asset locale and additional metadata information are optional fields.
